{"tid":309424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警主動CALL齊記者見面　女督察臨門拒答提問","createTime":"2017-07-05T04:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T05:28:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fca7ddc1a7af9eceece91204895b4c734195d1e","tid":309424,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170705/large/1499226580_0817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499226580_0817.jpg&h=dd00a7a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n健康顧問文耀輝施用「氟硝西泮」迷藥將德國女子迷姦被判囚12年，警方今早於未判刑前通知各傳媒，指案件主管旺角區重案組女督察林碧嘉將於判刑後會見傳媒，著傳媒於指定時間在高院門外等候，惟判刑後林在庭外講述完本案案情後，表示不評論判刑，並拒絕回答記者提問，包括女士如何防範被迷姦性侵等等，當記者不停追問時，林邊拒絕回答，邊匆匆上車離開。"},{"pid":"f24c718fcb56d4cb5e525818e848f7719b7b9a0f","tid":309424,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56915936&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56915936%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170705&d=%2F%2FQmoH%2FgMcs2fxRgan34XpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=33374a52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56915936%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170705&h=75a2c4f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56915936&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170705</a>"},{"pid":"e974b48ae4e6ab1d07e3881a8cbcf971fb41d798","tid":309424,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ffb23a0d08b6cffda8bb417b4a27b5d0494c2d","tid":309424,"uid":36551,"l